------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Loops can be nested, even if the array is more sophisticated, like with an
associative key containing the sub array.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{% for i in v1 %}{% for j in i.sub %}{{ j }}{% endfor %}{% endfor %}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{"v1": [{"sub": [1, 2], "something_else": [4, 5, 6]}, {"sub": [3]}]}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
